= Reach Beyond Time

Every time the world is remade anew, splinters and frayed threads of the previous timelines are left adrift in the the void. While most of them quickly diverge beyond recognition, some may yet be within the reach of our Edicts, should we deign to issue them. Whether or not it would be wise to do so is a hotly debated matter, both with and without the Cabal. 

