@land_reform
title: As Never So Always
subtitle: Align the lost threads with our weave. -1 power
unavailable-subtitle: [? if budget <= 0 : Our power reserve is drained. ?] [? if judicial_reform < 2 : The chains of causality are too strong. ?]
choose-if: judicial_reform >= 2 and budget > 0
on-arrival: budget -= 1; land_reform += 1; coalition_dissent += 1; rural_spd += 5*(1-dissent); rural_nsdap -= 4*(1-dissent); unemployed -= 1 if unemployed >= 5; dvp_relation -= 5; z_relation -= 4; left_strength += 8; left_dissent -= 5; rural_sol += 3; rural_policy += 1; coup_progress += 1; agriculture_goal_completed += 1;
max-visits: 4

We cannot undo what shall never be done, but we can alter the margins of history to create the missing context for it. Our edicts bring much-needed change to both sides of the divide, although that change is neither easy nor painless.


@agricultural_finance
title: Bleed Now's Veins Into Tomorrow
subtitle: Stabilize the weakest shards. -1 power
unavailable-subtitle: [? if budget <= 0 : Our power reserve is drained. ?]
choose-if: budget >= 1
on-arrival: budget -= 1; agricultural_finance += 1; rural_spd += 5*(1-dissent); rural_nsdap -= 3*(1-dissent); peoples_party_support += 1; center_dissent += 5; left_dissent += 4; rural_sol += 4; rural_policy += 1; economic_growth += 0.2;

We have established new conduits to provide the time-lost with additional coherence and vitality, saving them from looming dissolution. Our Pagan and Hermetic scholars criticize this as a dereliction of our sacred duties to our own world.


