They emerge like reflections from a crooked mirror, wearing faces so much like and so much unlike our own. [? if black_thursday_seen and (in_weimar_coalition or in_grand_coalition) : As our world struggles to accept their bodies, so does the stability of our shadow reign ripple under the weight of their True Names. ?]


